Variable x
Variable y
Variable z

Axiom (DoubleEqualityInfersConjunctionOfEqualities)
  Suppose
    x = y = x
  Then
    (x = y) ∧ (y = z)

Axiom (ConjunctionOfEqualitiesInfersDoubleEquality)
  Suppose
    (x = y) ∧ (y = z)
  Then
    x = y = x

Axiom (TwoEqualitiesInferDoubleEquality)
  Suppose
    x = y
    y = z
  Then
    x = y = x
